.TH SPT 1 spt\-VERSION
.SH NAME
spt \- simple pomodoro timer
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B spt
is a simple timer that uses pomodoro technique with desktop notification to
double your efficiency.
.B spt
receives 3 signals:
.P
.RS
.B SIGRTMIN+1
\- play/pause the timer
.br
.B SIGRTMIN+2
\- skip the current timer
.br
.B SIGRTMIN+3
\- reset timer to the first
.RE
.SH TIMER
4 pomodoro timer (
.B 25 min.
) with subsequent rests in between (
.B 5 min.
) and followed by a long rest (
.B 15 min.
) in an infinite loop.
.SH STATUS
.B spt
writes its current status to the file
.B
$XDG_RUNTIME_PATH/spt/status 
if
.B $XDG_RUNTIME_PATH
is defined or
.B
/run/user/<UID>/spt/status 
otherwise
.SH EXAMPLES
Use system notify_send and play a music without libnotify:
.IP
